### Health check
# Returns 200 if the service is running
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Readiness check
# Returns 200 if database is reachable, 503 otherwise
GET http://localhost:3000/ready

### Health check with compression
# Request with Accept-Encoding header
GET http://localhost:3000/health
Accept-Encoding: gzip

### OpenAPI JSON spec
# Returns the raw OpenAPI 3.0 JSON specification
GET http://localhost:3000/api-doc/openapi.json

### Swagger UI
# Open in browser: http://localhost:3000/swagger-ui
